  The Foundation is Now Complete

  The 7 activity domains are now fully established in the DSL:

  1. Tasks - What I need to DO
  2. Habits - What I need to REPEAT
  3. Goals - What I want to ACHIEVE
  4. Events - What I need to ATTEND
  5. Principles - What I BELIEVE/VALUE
  6. Choices - What I need to DECIDE
  7. Finance - What I SPEND/EARN

  This provides the vocabulary for SKUEL's domain-specific language. As you noted, an LLM can now serve as a natural language bridge to this structured vocabulary - understanding user intent and mapping it to the appropriate domain
  context.

